</span></p><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-jHkVzv gbyaRg pf-55_"><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bQtKYq wvgEH pf-56_"><b>Vasodilation</b> - Blood vessels near the skin open up to release heat to the surroundings, lowering blood pressure. 
